this will install laravel breeze and auth login etc

php artisan breeze:install

Add the following fields to user table migrattion

 $table->string('photo')->nullable();
            $table->string('role')->default('user');
            $table->string('status')->default('1'); 

Php artisan migrate

Now cutomize its login screen register and home page

Now if we php artisan route:list we notice that login get route is going to AUthenticationSessionController store method so customize it 

as the the default login page is auth folder so we will create a page Admin_Auth.blade.php

and we will copy all the assets and other requirment even dashboard design to public folder and link its css and js to this Admin_Auth.blade.php then we will extend
its login dashboard and other register page

DO it by yourself get help from php artisan route:list
